Class Jarvis

  • java.lang.Object
    • deeplearningGroup1.Jarvis

  • public class Jarvis
extends java.lang.Object
    Jarvis is the neural network essay grading class through the use of a trained neural network, consisting of a list of Neural Layers with associated weights and biases
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Steven Rose
    See Also:
    NeuralLayer, Matrix, Essay
